---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import placeholder from "@images/placeholder.png";
---

<section class="about">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Meet Dan, Your Local Handyman</h2>
        <p>
            Call Dan began with one simple goal in mind. Dan wanted to provide
            straightforward and affordable handyman services to homeowners and
            businesses across South West Sydney. After recognising the need for
            trustworthy handyman services in areas like Penrith, Campbelltown,
            and Liverpool, Dan built the business on reliability, fair pricing,
            and quality workmanship. Over the years, locals have come to count
            on Call Dan for everything from gutter cleaning and mould removal to
            fixing leaky taps and window cleaning. Today, the business continues
            to grow through genuine referrals and satisfied repeat customers,
            making Call Dan a trusted name in local handyman services.
        </p>
        <Image
            src={placeholder}
            alt="handyman south sydney"
            class="about-image"
        />
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2rem;
        color: white;
    }
    h2 {
        font-size: 1.65rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .about-image {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        h2 {
            grid-area: title;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }
        .about-image {
            grid-area: image;
        }
        p {
            grid-area: text-content;
        }
        .container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            grid-template-areas:
                "title title"
                "image text-content";
        }
    }

    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
        h2 {
            font-size: 3rem;
        }
        .container {
            gap: 3rem;
        }
    }
</style>
